---
// Pricing/How We Work Section - Plain text, minimal cards
---

<section id="pricing" class="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="headline">Two meetings. One clear path forward.</h2>
    <p class="intro-text">
      Start your app's day-1 with us. Our engagement process is simple and transparent.
    </p>

    <div class="meetings">
      <div class="meeting">
        <div class="meeting-header">
          <span class="meeting-number">1</span>
          <h3>Free Brief <span class="subtitle">— Your Story</span></h3>
        </div>
        <p>
          Tell us about your business, your challenge, your vision. We listen, we ask questions, we start understanding your patterns.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>No cost, no commitment</li>
          <li>NDA available if needed</li>
          <li>60-90 minutes of focused discussion</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="meeting">
        <div class="meeting-header">
          <span class="meeting-number">2</span>
          <h3>The Proposal <span class="subtitle">— Our Plan</span></h3>
        </div>
        <p>
          We present a complete working plan—from foundation discovery through your final BRS. You'll see exactly how we'll uncover what you need.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Detailed discovery roadmap</li>
          <li>Timeline and process breakdown</li>
          <li>PoC plan customized for your project</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="outcome">
      <h3>The Outcome</h3>
      <p>
        Time-based contract. Typically 5-7 PoCs to reach solid requirements. You receive a Business Requirements Specification that doesn't just describe features—it explains why they matter and how they serve your strategy.
      </p>
      <p class="highlight">
        This BRS becomes your development team's north star.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background-color: var(--color-base);
    padding: var(--space-5xl) var(--space-xl);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: var(--max-width-text);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .headline {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .meetings {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .meeting-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .meeting-number {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--color-terracotta);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 700;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .meeting h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .meeting p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .meeting ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
  }

  .meeting li {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .meeting li::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--color-cyan);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .outcome {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  }

  .outcome h3 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .outcome p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .outcome .highlight {
    color: var(--color-terracotta);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .pricing {
      padding: var(--space-4xl) var(--space-lg);
    }

    .headline {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }

    .meeting-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }

    .meeting ul {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
